	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Business Directory contact listing lists all business contacts.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Adding A Contact</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Click on the <strong>New Contact </strong>button to create new business contact. See Help on Adding New Contact.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Creating A Distribution List</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Click on the <strong>New Distribution List</strong> button to create new business distribution list. See Help on Creating New Contact.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Deleting A Contact</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To delete a business contact, put a tick in checkbox at selected contact.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Delete</strong> button. A confirmation pop-up message will appear before the contact is deleted. Click on the <strong>OK</strong> button to delete or <strong>Cancel</strong> button to cancel.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Send Message</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To send a message to a business contact, put a tick in checkbox at selected contact.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Send Message</strong> button, it will direct you to Compose Message page with all the e-mail(s)selected in the <strong>To</strong> field.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Move Contact</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">A Business contact can be moved from a folder to another.</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To move a business contact, put a tick in checkbox at selected contact.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select the target folder to move to, from the <strong>Folder</strong> list.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Move</strong> button to move the contact to the targetted folder.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
